OL,3,CHappy hour ban lifted: Pubs and clubs
OL,4,Cable to offer alcohol promos
OL,6,FRestaurants, bars, clubs and other
OL,7,Fhospitality venues in Jersey will be
OL,8,Fable to offer alcoholic drink
OL,9,Fpromotions after an almost 40-year ban
OL,10,Fto protect public health was
OL,11,Foverturned.
OL,13,FFrom Friday 30 May, 'on-trade'
OL,14,Fbusinesses can advertise discounted
OL,15,Fdeals such as 'Happy Hour',
OL,16,F'Bottomless Brunch' and 2-for-1
OL,17,Fcocktails.
OL,19,FThe rule to block promotions had been
OL,20,Fin place since 1987 to try and curb
OL,21,Fexcessive alcohol consumption.
