OL,4,Cable to offer alcohol promos
OL,6,FHowever, concerns had been raised over
OL,7,Frecent years about the rise in at-home
OL,8,Fand pre-drinks as people avoided
OL,9,Fhigher costs at the bar by opting for
OL,10,Fcheaper prices in shops and off-
OL,11,Flicences.
OL,13,FThe Jersey Hospitality Association
OL,14,F(JHO) wrote to the Attorney General
OL,15,F(AG) earlier this year and following
OL,16,Fhis recommendation to lift the ban, a
OL,17,Fchange in the rules has now been
OL,18,Fagreed by the Licensing Authority.
