OL,3,CHappy hour ban lifted: Pubs and clubs
OL,4,Cable to offer alcohol promos
OL,6,FMarcus Calvani, Co-Chief Executive
OL,7,FOfficer of the JHO, says: "Across the
OL,8,Fboard, rises in costs have meant that
OL,9,Fpubs, bars and restaurants were being
OL,10,Fsignificantly undercut by off-licence
OL,11,Ftraders, leading people to buy cheap
OL,12,Falcohol in shops and drink
OL,13,Fsignificantly more than if they were
OL,14,Fout meeting friends.
OL,16,F"This is great news for Jersey as we
OL,17,Fwant to see people back in licensed
OL,18,Fpremises, supporting the visitor
OL,19,Feconomy and encouraging responsible
OL,20,Fsocial interaction."
