OL,6,FThe updated Licensing Law states that
OL,7,Fthe AG will still intervene if there
OL,8,Fis evidence that promotions
OL,9,F"encourage, or are likely to
OL,10,Fencourage, customers to drink to
OL,11,Fexcess".
OL,13,FThe police will also continue to
OL,14,Fmonitor licensed premises and check
OL,15,Fadverts, reporting back to the AG.
